2.1 The optimal deployment method is the install-free deployment via uvx (`uvx osm-mcp-server`) because:
- It doesn't require manual installation of the package
- It uses the stdio communication method (standard for MCP servers)
- It's specifically designed for MCP hosts and is the simplest approach

