## Development

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/gerred/mcp-server-replicate.git
cd mcp-server-replicate
```

2. Install development dependencies:

```bash
uv pip install --system ".[dev]"
```

3. Install pre-commit hooks:

```bash
pre-commit install
```

4. Run tests:

```bash
pytest
```

